Package: vijPlots
Type: Package
Title: vijPlots: Yet Another jamovi Plotting Module
Version: 1.2.2
Author: Vincent Jalby
Maintainer: Vincent Jalby <vincent.jalby@unilim.fr>
Description: Main statistical charts (histogram, boxplot, point, bar, line, 
    raincloud…) with many options along with Likert plot, multiple response barplot,
    Principal Component and (Multiple) Correspondence Analyses. 
    The module is available in the <strong>Plots</strong> tab.
    Project source (and changelog) is available at  
    <a href="https://github.com/vjalby/vijPlots" target="_blank">Github</a>.
License: GPL (>=2)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: jmvcore (>= 0.8.5), R6, psych, MASS, tidyr, dplyr, tibble, ggplot2, 
         labelled, scales, ggstats, ggh4x, ggdist, ggpp, ggrepel, ggforce,
         fitdistrplus, dichromat, colorspace, qqplotr, forcats, GPArotation, 
         FactoMineR, 
         
